text: Hennepin County ( ) is a county in the U.S. state of Minnesota. As of the 2020 census the population was 1,281,565. It is the most populous county in Minnesota and the 35th-most populous county in the United States. Its county seat is Minneapolis. ==References== Category:Minnesota counties Category:1852 establishments in the United States Category:1850s establishments in Minnesota Territory
